Relics are permanent items that give a passive bonus for the duration of the run. Most relics can be obtained regardless of the character you are playing. Each character has 9 Relics that can only be obtained by them.

Starter Relics are given to each character when beginning a run. This starter relic can later be replaced with an upgraded {{QueryLink|Relics|rarity:Ancient|Ancient|2}} version by picking up the {{R|Touch of Orobas||2}} from the {{2|Ancients|Ancient}} {{KW|Orobas||2}} at the start of [[StS2:Acts#Act 2|Act 2]], when offered.
